Tool use	No custom MCP tool	Custom MCP-style tool analyze_student_load created and exposed to the model
Autonomous decision-making	The app mostly calculated the plan through fixed logic	The LLM chooses SCHEDULE_MODE, RECOVERY_MODE, TRIAGE_MODE, or WARNING_MODE
